data.description: This beautifully renovated 3132 sq ft Craftsman is just 10 minutes from Redstone Arsenal with NO HOA. 5 spacious bedrooms (includes 2 ensuites), 3 baths, open floor plan, custom cabinets, granite & quartz countertops, gorgeous dual-head tiled shower, and huge bonus room. This home offers the ability to enjoy outdoor living at its best with 3 porches and 2 balconies, 30x40 3-bay shop, and 8x8 storm shelter. Recent upgrades include plumbing, electrical, HVAC, windows, skylights, paint, water heater, whole home water filtration system, and flooring ensuring a contemporary and stylish living experience. Your dream home awaits at 172 Airport Road, Laceys Spring!
